HOPE ENGLISH SCHOOL - MOBILE APPLICATION APK
=============================================
Package: com.subraimission.app
Wrapper: Capacitor Native Android Engine v8.0
Target Platform: Android 10+ (API Level 29+)

This is the direct APK bundle download entry point for the Hope English School system. 
Upon production compilation on your Windows/Mac build server, replace this informational manifest file with your actual compiled 'app-debug.apk' or 'app-release.apk' binary.

Windows Quick Build Instructions:
---------------------------------
1. Make sure Android Studio & Java 17 JDK are installed.
2. In your project root, run:
   npm run build
   npx cap sync
3. Walk into the android directory and build with Gradle Wrapper:
   cd android
   .\gradlew assembleDebug
4. Retrieve the fully installable APK package at:
   .\android\app\build\outputs\apk\debug\app-debug.apk
5. Copy 'app-debug.apk' to your web server's public folder as 'Hope_English_School.apk' to enable instant downloads!
